160
00:15:31,190 --> 00:15:37,330
Yeah, yeah, that's right, huh? I hate
gym and math, but art is my best subject!

161
00:15:37,370 --> 00:15:38,330
For me, it's science.

162
00:15:38,370 --> 00:15:41,330
–What about you, Ena?
–I've never been to school.

163
00:15:41,370 --> 00:15:46,330
Oh, that's right. The tsunami
happened before Ena started school.

164
00:15:46,370 --> 00:15:50,100
Do you guys... want to go to school?

165
00:15:50,140 --> 00:15:52,040
Not especially. Who needs studying?

166
00:15:52,080 --> 00:15:55,020
If you go to the institution,
you can do all you like.

167
00:15:55,880 --> 00:15:58,210
No way, that place smells like medicine!

168
00:15:58,250 --> 00:16:00,720
Yeah, that goes for me, too. No way.

169
00:16:00,760 --> 00:16:03,590
And someone who's
escaped from there ought to know!

170
00:16:05,030 --> 00:16:09,160
I know! How about we all
drive to Gohan's house tomorrow?

171
00:16:09,200 --> 00:16:09,720
Cool!

172
00:16:09,760 --> 00:16:12,170
That will be fun! Let's go, let's go!

173
