O-Oh, no!

181
00:17:12,390 --> 00:17:13,990
Hey, get out!

182
00:17:32,350 --> 00:17:34,320
Ow! Ow!

183
00:17:38,190 --> 00:17:39,750
Chiko!

184
00:17:39,790 --> 00:17:41,480
Come quietly!

185
00:17:41,520 --> 00:17:42,580
Damn!

186
00:18:14,020 --> 00:18:15,320
Gohan, this way!

187
00:18:15,360 --> 00:18:16,320
But everyone else is–!

188
00:18:16,360 --> 00:18:17,620
Just come on!

189
00:18:18,790 --> 00:18:20,320
–Piegero!
–Gohan!

190
00:18:20,360 --> 00:18:21,160
Piegero!

191
00:18:21,200 --> 00:18:22,720
What are you doing?!

192
00:18:26,200 --> 00:18:28,330
Hey, you!

193
00:18:31,810 --> 00:18:34,400
Piegero!

194
00:19:13,380 --> 00:19:15,340
Why?! Huh?

195
00:19:15,380 --> 00:19:17,750
