and already they're delinquents.

199
00:19:28,560 --> 00:19:31,260
They're too young for that!

200
00:19:33,770 --> 00:19:38,170
You're no ordinary kid, huh?
You're incredibly strong.

201
00:19:38,210 --> 00:19:39,330
Are you going back there?

202
00:19:39,370 --> 00:19:45,610
No. There's nobody there, even if I
did go back. See ya. Respect your mom.

203
00:19:46,780 --> 00:19:48,940
Thanks, Piegero<i>-san.</i>

