<i>Aah, enough! Even Kami-sama has it rough.</i>

225
00:23:45,490 --> 00:23:47,620
<i>So sorry.</i>

226
00:23:47,660 --> 00:23:52,720
<i>Ooh, full-bellied ZENKAI power!</i>

227
00:23:55,460 --> 00:24:00,700
<i>Come on out, full-on ZENKAI power!</i>

228
00:24:12,250 --> 00:24:14,180
<i>Heya! I'm Goku!</i>

229
00:24:14,220 --> 00:24:15,310
<i>Tenshinhan and the others</i>

230
